{"tid":1244321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佩洛西：若香港與中國大陸無異將不會再享有特權","createTime":"2019-06-20T00:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T09:06:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":97,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"d429c67e9e7dfe392c681214b36e49701edaedf9","tid":1244321,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:30:45.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院議長，民主黨的佩洛西支持早前有跨黨派國會議員提出《香港人權與民主法》草案，要求美國每年檢視香港的自治情況，以維持美國對香港的特殊待遇。<br />\n<br />\n她指在《香港政策法》下，現時美國將香港視為獨立的經濟和關稅區，享有內地沒有的特權，如果有關法案通過，美國會假設一國兩制已經失效，總統特朗普和聯邦政府，需要具體證明香港在政治、法治和經濟等方面，依然有別於內地，香港才可以繼續享有特殊地位。<br />\n<br />\n佩洛西強調，如果香港的情況與內地無分別，就不會有特權，但沒有提及何時會推動通過有關法案。"},{"pid":"6c84373b356e64c449f46fa1f980798bcaf13e37","tid":1244321,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:30:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1125623&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1125623%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZVysXiw7s3azMdswkJgtbARqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=bc00daaf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1125623&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"564ea90ac3130f6df1ea21b3b2ee10058c842c5c","tid":1244321,"uid":50457,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:31:38.000Z","msg":"具體證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d471884dff63cf6a852d038ec4e8d72cc27981d","tid":1244321,"uid":108337,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:32:26.000Z","msg":"制裁香港 人人有責"},{"pid":"86259f0ee6c3a42e391a948645246032d3a0e938","tid":1244321,"uid":25601,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:34:19.000Z","msg":"制裁香港 香港變臭港"},{"pid":"49d9bb719d46126ee398983f5a367ff721f6c06a","tid":1244321,"uid":3508,"like":38,"dislike":0,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"repl